# MagicSquare Project Baseline

- Project name: `MagicSquare`
- Language: `Python` (`3.10+`)
- Architecture pattern: `ECB` (Boundary -> Control -> Entity)
- Test strategy: `Dual-Track TDD`
- Coverage target: at least `80%`

# Working Expectations

- Check existing related tests before writing or modifying implementation.
- Identify the target ECB layer before coding.
- Keep all generated code aligned with project test strategy and architecture.
- Warn explicitly when a request would break these constraints.
